These results will probably be the most accurate I'll ever report as conditions at the time they were taken were absolutely ideal. While I did select a water color- it was actually almost colorless.
Calm- only one other boat on lake.  Deep hole is in the middle of a fairly narrow channel. It's July Fourth weekend. I lucked out with a lull in boat traffic on a beautiful- sunny day.
